Transforming the image:
Left Mouse + drag - pan
Right Mouse + drag / Mousewheel - zoom
f : zoom to fit
1 : zoom to 1:1
+ : zoom in
- : zoom out

Editing Exposure (via glsl)
g + drag : gain (contrast)
o + drag : offset (exposure)
v + drag : gamma
c : toggle colormap

Display:
- Image coordinates
- pixel values
- Current zoom level
